\pard\keepn\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\s5\sb120\sa60\kerning0\ul\b\f0\fs28 Course Objective\par
\pard\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\kerning1\ulnone\b0\f1\fs24 Learn how & when to use embedded microcontrollers by studying & experimenting with the TI MSP430 Development Kit.  By the end of the course, a conscientious student should be able to apply the basic capabilities of the MSP430 microcontroller to simple IOT devices and robots and to control devices like solar/battery systems, home automation, remote meters and sensors, and smartphone accessories.\par
\par
